text: A member is a person who belongs to a group of people. Member may also mean: * In set theory, an object that belongs to a set (mathematical) is an element, * A user that is signed up for an internet service provider (ISP) service is a member of the ISP * Military jury, which is called "Members" by those in the military * Limb, a part of the human or animal body * The penis (slang)
title: Member
